94th days.
2021.01.24(Sunday).

How about these pants?
이 바지 어때?

Will they fit? I’m going to try them on.
잘 맞을까? 한번 입어봐야 겠다.

I think they fit you well.
내가 볼 땐 너한테 잘 맞는 것 같은데.

Fortunately, they fit me well. I like the color and style, too!
다행히도 나한테 잘 맞아. 색깔과 스타일도 맘에 들어!

I thought you gained weight, but I’m glad they fit you.
너 살찐 줄 알았는데 맞아서 다행이다.

I actually gained 1 to 2 kilograms, but luckily they fit me well.
실제로 1-2 킬로그램이나 쪘는데 다행히 잘 맞아.

Even if you gain more weight, your belt will be flexible and comfortable.
살이 더 찌더라도, 허리띠가 신축성이 있어서 편할 거야.

Right! I knew that for the first time.
그러네! 처음 알았어.

Make sure if it is flexible the next time you’re shopping alone.
다음에 혼자 쇼필갈 때는 신축성이 있는지 꼭 확인해.

Ok. You’re so smart. It was good to go shopping with you.
알았어. 넌 정말 똑똑해. 너와 쇼핑하러 오니까 좋았어.



